# RK3399Pro NPU Driver — Kconfig/Makefile

config EDGE_AI_NPU
	tristate "RK3399Pro NPU Driver"
	depends on ARCH_ROCKCHIP || COMPILE_TEST
	select DMA_CMA
	select DMA_SHARED_BUFFER
	help
	  Rockchip RK3399Pro Neural Processing Unit (NPU) driver.
	  This enables the /dev/rknpu misc device for AI inference
	  acceleration on the RK1808 NPU IP core.

	  The NPU provides:
	    - 3.0 TOPS INT8 peak performance
	    - 1920 MAC units @ 800MHz
	    - 256KB on-chip SRAM
	    - Support for CNN, RNN, LSTM networks

	  To compile this driver as a module, choose M here:
	  the module will be called rknpu.

	  If unsure, say Y.
